<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title></title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-+0n0xVW2eSR5OomGNYDnhzAbDsOXxcvSN1TPprVMTNDbiYZCxYbOOl7+AMvyTG2x" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/materialize.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app-styles.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>

<body>
  <div id="video-card" class="card">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Please read carefully!</h1>
      <p>

        Test running time: approx. 17 minutes <br><br>

        Please make sure to fill out the form below. You can either fill it out before
        clicking (Start Measurement), or while the measurement is running. <br><br>

        Once finished, the results will automatically be downloaded as a text file. <br>
        Please share this file with Ufuk Cetinkaya (cetinkaya@dipf.de) (Subject: Measurements) <br><br>

        You can either use your own webcam (please remain seated in front of the computer
        for the test, look into the direction of the camera). <br><br>

        Alternatively, we provide a video which can be used as input for a virtual webcam. Please
        make sure to select the correct webcam / virtual webcam before running the test. <br><br>

        If you don't know what a virtual webcam is / how it works, please read this: <a href="https://restream.io/integrations/obs-studio/how-to-use-obs-virtual-camera/">Virtual Webcam in OBS</a> 
        <br><br>

        Thank you for your participation! :) <br><br>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <video id="video-input" autoplay playsinline width="480px" height="360px" style="transform: scaleX(-1)"></video>
        <img id="image-input" hidden width="480px" height="360px"/>
        <canvas id="canvas-combined-plot" style="display: none" width="480px" height="360px"></canvas>
        <canvas id="canvas-input" style="display: none" width="480px" height="360px"></canvas>
        <canvas id="canvas-cropped" style="display: none" width="112px" height="112px"></canvas>
        <canvas id="canvas-landmark-plot" style="display: none" width="112px" height="112px"></canvas>
    </div>
    <select id="camera-select-box" name="camera_select_box">
        <option value="" disabled selected></option>
    </select>
    <label for="username">Your Name:</label>
    <input type="text" name="username" id="input-username">
    <label for="laptop-desktop">Laptop/Desktop/Phone/Tablet?:</label>
    <select name="laptop-desktop" id="input-laptop-desktop">
      <option value="laptop">Laptop</option>
      <option value="desktop">Desktop</option>
      <option value="phone">Phone</option>
      <option value="tablet">Tablet</option>
    </select>
    <label for="device-name">Device Name (e.g. ThinkPad T420):</label>
    <input type="text" name="device-name" id="input-device-name">
    <label for="os">Operating System (if possible provide version number):</label>
    <input type="text" name="os" id="input-os">
    <label for="cpu">CPU (e.g. Core i5 8550U):</label>
    <input type="text" name="cpu" id="input-cpu">
    <label for="gpu">GPU (if you have a discrete GPU):</label>
    <input type="text" name="gpu" id="input-gpu">
    <label for="ram">RAM:</label>
    <input type="text" name="ram" id="input-ram">
    <label for="browser">Browser:</label>
    <input type="text" name="browser" id="input-browser">
    <label for="webcam">Normal Webcam or Virtual Webcam:</label>
    <select name="webcam" id="input-webcam" required>
      <option value="real">Real Webcam</option>
      <option value="virtual">Virtual Webcam</option>
    </select>

    <button id="start-measurement">Start Measurement</button>
  </div>
</body>
</html>


<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/hacktimer@1.1.3/HackTimer.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@vladmandic/face-api/dist/face-api.js"></script>
<script src="https://www.lactame.com/lib/image-js/0.21.2/image.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/simple-hog.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/performance-test.js" charset="utf-8"></script>

</html>
